<item>
            <title>[LU-11845] Support encrypted ZFS volumes</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11845</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osd-zfs does not call dmu_objset_own() with decrypt=B_TRUE, so we can&apos;t mount encrypted ZFS volumes.&#160; This should be a simple fix of passing &lt;tt&gt;B_TRUE&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;dmu_objset_own()&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;dmu_objset_disown()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
